          "t.player_eye_height = 1.620001; return (q.is_gliding || q.is_swimming || q.is_crawling || q.can_damage_nearby_mobs) ? ((0.6 / 2) - t.player_eye_height) : ((1.8 / 2) - t.player_eye_height);",
